data.description: Discover elegance in every detail with this stunning residence located in the prestigious Bentwater subdivision. Boasting new floors and fresh paint throughout, this home offers a modern aesthetic that seamlessly blends with its upscale surroundings. Entertain effortlessly in the updated kitchen and unwind by one of two cozy fireplaces. The primary bath features a separate tub and shower for ultimate relaxation, while the upstairs jack and jill layout, along with updated vanities, ensures comfort and convenience for all. With a partially finished basement and updated light fixtures adding to the allure, this home epitomizes luxury living at its finest. Don't miss the opportunity to make this your own retreat.
